items.desc: Welcome to the Yami no Matsuei Wiki, a wiki about the Yami no Matsuei series! The story follows the investigations of Asato Tsuzuki and Hisoka Kurosaki, two shinigamis whose job is to makes sure that those who are dead remain dead and stay in their proper realms. With each case they investigate, they come closer to the conspiracies of the serial killer Dr. Kazutaka Muraki and the secrets of Tsuzuki's own dark past!
